item.title: CVE-2019-3704|2024-08-04T19:19:18.184Z -- dell%20emc -- vnx%20control%20station%20in%20dell%20emc%20vnx2%20oe%20for%20file
item.description: VNX Control Station in Dell EMC VNX2 OE for File versions prior to 8.1.9.236 contains OS command injection vulnerability. Due to inadequate restriction configured in sudores, a local authenticated malicious user could potentially execute arbitrary OS commands as root by exploiting this vulnerability.
